data.description:
FRESH NEW PAINT AS OF DEC 2!!
Welcome to your new sanctuary! This exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers 1924 square feet of comfortable living space, complete with a dedicated office for work or creativity. The expansive three-car garage provides ample space for vehicles and additional storage.

As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the stunning open stone wall that gracefully opens the kitchen to the living room, creating an inviting and cohesive space for gatherings. The spacious bedrooms provide ample room for rest and relaxation, while the master suite boasts a generous walk-in closet, ensuring you have all the storage you need.

Step outside into your own private retreat. The backyard features a large seating area, perfect for entertaining guests or simply unwinding after a long day. A fire pit sets the mood for cozy evenings under the stars, and a magnificent pergola extends the patio, creating an enchanting outdoor living space for all seasons.

In addition to the wonderful amenities of this property, residents of this community have exclusive access to a refreshing pool, offering a perfect escape from the summer heat. Multiple neighborhood parks provide additional opportunities for recreation and leisure.

With an annual HOA fee of $280, you'll enjoy the benefits of a well-maintained community and shared amenities.

Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your new home. Schedule a visit today and experience the magic for yourself!
